---
const pillars = [
  {
    name: 'Digital',
    description: 'Nostalgia 8-bit, precisión tecnológica y la estética retro como lenguaje.',
    iconColor: 'digital',
    titleColor: 'text-digital-500',
  },
  {
    name: 'Natural',
    description: 'Maderas nativas argentinas, sustentabilidad y la riqueza de nuestra tierra.',
    iconColor: 'natural',
    titleColor: 'text-natural-500',
  },
  {
    name: 'Humano',
    description: 'Calidez artesanal, conexión emocional y tecnología que se siente viva.',
    iconColor: 'human',
    titleColor: 'text-human-500',
  },
];
---

<section class="view view--hidden" id="historia">
  <!-- Decorative texture -->
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.04]" aria-hidden="true"
    style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 width=%224%22 height=%224%22><rect width=%224%22 height=%224%22 fill=%22%23a0a09b%22 opacity=%220.5%22/><rect width=%222%22 height=%222%22 fill=%22%23c9d1c9%22 opacity=%220.3%22/></svg>'); background-size: 4px 4px;">
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-1 flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 lg:px-10">
    <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-5xl">
      <div data-enter class="mb-6 text-center lg:mb-8">
        <p class="t-text-muted mb-2 font-[var(--font-mono)] text-[length:var(--text-mono-sm)] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
          Nuestra historia
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-[length:var(--text-h1)] font-semibold leading-tight">
          Donde lo digital se encuentra con lo natural
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div data-enter class="mx-auto mb-5 max-w-2xl text-center sm:mb-8 lg:mb-10">
        <p class="t-text-2 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed sm:text-[length:var(--text-body)]">
          Tecleados nace de una idea simple pero profunda: que la tecnología puede sentirse
          viva. Cada teclado fusiona la nostalgia digital de la era 8-bit con la calidez de las
          maderas nativas argentinas y el cuidado artesanal de manos humanas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div data-enter class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 sm:gap-4 lg:gap-6">
        {pillars.map((pillar) => (
          <div class="t-bg-elevated t-border group rounded-xl border p-3 text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-md sm:p-5 lg:p-6">
            <div class="mb-2 flex justify-center sm:mb-3">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" class="h-8 w-8 pixel-art transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 sm:h-12 sm:w-12">
                {pillar.iconColor === 'digital' && (
                  <>
                    <rect x="8" y="8" width="16" height="16" fill="var(--color-digital-500)" opacity="0.9"/>
                    <rect x="10" y="10" width="12" height="12" fill="var(--color-digital-700)"/>
                    <rect x="12" y="12" width="8" height="8" fill="var(--color-digital-400)"/>
                    <rect x="14" y="14" width="4" height="4" fill="var(--color-digital-200)"/>
                    <rect x="12" y="4" width="2" height="4" fill="var(--color-digital-500)"/>
                    <rect x="18" y="4" width="2" height="4" fill="var(--color-digital-500)"/>
                    <rect x="12" y="24" width="2" height="4" fill="var(--color-digital-500)"/>
                    <rect x="18" y="24" width="2" height="4" fill="var(--color-digital-500)"/>
                    <rect x="4" y="12" width="4" height="2" fill="var(--color-digital-500)"/>
                    <rect x="4" y="18" width="4" height="2" fill="var(--color-digital-500)"/>
                    <rect x="24" y="12" width="4" height="2" fill="var(--color-digital-500)"/>
                    <rect x="24" y="18" width="4" height="2" fill="var(--color-digital-500)"/>
                  </>
                )}
                {pillar.iconColor === 'natural' && (
                  <>
                    <rect x="14" y="22" width="4" height="8" fill="var(--color-human-600)"/>
                    <rect x="10" y="16" width="12" height="6" fill="var(--color-natural-500)"/>
                    <rect x="8" y="10" width="16" height="6" fill="var(--color-natural-400)"/>
                    <rect x="12" y="4" width="8" height="6" fill="var(--color-natural-300)"/>
                    <rect x="14" y="2" width="4" height="4" fill="var(--color-natural-500)"/>
                  </>
                )}
                {pillar.iconColor === 'human' && (
                  <>
                    <rect x="8" y="16" width="16" height="12" fill="var(--color-human-500)"/>
                    <rect x="10" y="18" width="4" height="4" fill="var(--color-human-300)"/>
                    <rect x="18" y="18" width="4" height="4" fill="var(--color-human-300)"/>
                    <rect x="14" y="22" width="4" height="6" fill="var(--color-human-700)"/>
                    <polygon points="16,4 4,16 28,16" fill="var(--color-human-400)"/>
                    <polygon points="16,6 6,16 26,16" fill="var(--color-human-600)"/>
                  </>
                )}
              </svg>
            </div>

            <h3 class:list={['mb-0.5 text-sm font-semibold sm:mb-1 sm:text-[length:var(--text-h3)]', pillar.titleColor]}>
              {pillar.name}
            </h3>
            <p class="t-text-2 hidden text-sm font-light leading-relaxed sm:block">
              {pillar.description}
            </p>
            <p class="t-text-2 text-[10px] font-light leading-snug sm:hidden">
              {pillar.description}
            </p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <p data-enter class="t-text-muted mt-6 text-center font-[var(--font-mono)] text-[length:var(--text-mono-sm)]">
        // compiled: buenos aires, argentina
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <span class="dev-annotation absolute bottom-16 left-4">// view: historia | pillars: 3</span>
</section>
